                    <p class="text-xs text-[var(--muted)] mt-3">Response = 50%+ improvement on standard rating scales. Remission = near-complete symptom resolution. Rates derived from published clinical trials. Individual outcomes vary. <a href="/treatments/" class="underline hover:text-[var(--accent)]">View treatment details</a></p>
